From: Luis Henriques <lhenriques@suse.com>
Date: Fri, 19 Jul 2019 15:32:22 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] ceph: fix buffer free while holding i_ceph_lock in
 fill_inode()
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.2.14
Git-commit: af8a85a41734f37b67ba8ce69d56b685bee4ac48

[ Upstream commit af8a85a41734f37b67ba8ce69d56b685bee4ac48 ]

Calling ceph_buffer_put() in fill_inode() may result in freeing the
i_xattrs.blob buffer while holding the i_ceph_lock.  This can be fixed by
postponing the call until later, when the lock is released.

